### 主题列表
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/topics?page=0&size=20
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: idea-stage4-topic-list

### 创建主题（重复执行前请修改 code 和 name）
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/topics
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: idea-stage4-topic-create

{
  "code": "IDEA_AI",
  "name": "IDEA 人工智能",
  "description": "通过 IDEA HTTP Client 创建的测试主题",
  "keywords": "人工智能,AI,大模型",
  "excludedKeywords": "广告",
  "color": "#2563EB",
  "icon": "cpu",
  "language": "zh-CN",
  "enabled": true,
  "sortOrder": 10
}

### 查询主题详情（将 1 替换为真实主题 ID）
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/topics/1
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: idea-stage4-topic-detail

### 停用主题（将 1 替换为真实主题 ID）
PATCH http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/topics/1/enabled
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: idea-stage4-topic-disable

{
  "enabled": false
}

### 采集源列表
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/sources?page=0&size=20
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: idea-stage4-source-list

### 创建采集源（topicIds 替换为真实主题 ID）
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/sources
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: idea-stage4-source-create

{
  "code": "IDEA_EXAMPLE_RSS",
  "name": "IDEA 示例 RSS",
  "type": "RSS",
  "homeUrl": "https://example.com",
  "feedUrl": "https://example.com/feed.xml",
  "language": "zh-CN",
  "charset": "UTF-8",
  "userAgent": "KnowledgeCollector/1.0 (+local-admin)",
  "timeoutSeconds": 15,
  "maxRetries": 2,
  "requestIntervalMillis": 2000,
  "obeyRobots": true,
  "fetchFullContent": true,
  "summaryOnly": false,
  "saveSnapshot": false,
  "enabled": true,
  "notes": "IDEA HTTP Client 测试数据",
  "topicIds": [1]
}

### 查询采集源详情（将 1 替换为真实来源 ID）
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/sources/1
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: idea-stage4-source-detail

### 测试来源边界（Stage 4 预期返回 422 和 SOURCE-TEST-NOT-AVAILABLE）
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/sources/1/test
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: idea-stage4-source-test

### 删除采集源（将 1 替换为真实来源 ID）
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/sources/1
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: idea-stage4-source-delete

### 删除主题（必须先删除或解除关联来源）
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/topics/1
Accept: application/json
X-Correlation-Id: idea-stage4-topic-delete
